OL,3,CPrince of Wales jokes he may ditch
OL,4,Cbeard for moustache after meeting
OL,5,Ctroops
OL,7,FThe Prince of Wales joked he might
OL,8,Fshave his beard and leave a moustache
OL,9,Fafter meeting a string of Army
OL,10,Fofficers sporting the on-trend facial
OL,11,Fhair.
OL,13,FPrince William made the quip when
OL,14,Fvisiting troops from the Mercian
OL,15,FRegiment at their barracks in
OL,16,FWiltshire in his role as their Colonel-
OL,17,Fin-Chief.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
