FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1774620679
OL,3,CPrince of Wales jokes he may ditch
OL,4,Cbeard for moustache after meeting
OL,5,Ctroops
OL,7,FWearing a camouflage uniform and the
OL,8,Fregimental beret, he met soldiers from
OL,9,Fthe 1st Battalion who returned last
OL,10,FDecember from a six-month deployment
OL,11,Fto Estonia as part of the UK's
OL,12,Fcontribution to Nato forces.
OL,14,FThe prince also spoke to a group of
OL,15,Ffemale soldiers who discussed issues
OL,16,Fthey face in the Army.
OL,18,FIn the officer's mess at Picton
OL,19,FBarracks, Bulford the future king
OL,20,Fchatted to officers and their families
OL,21,Fand shared a joke with many of them.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1774620679
OL,3,CPrince of Wales jokes he may ditch
OL,4,Cbeard for moustache after meeting
OL,5,Ctroops
OL,7,FLieutenant Jack Austin, 23, was
OL,8,Fsporting a moustache and said he
OL,9,Fmentioned the subject of his facial
OL,10,Fhair when chatting to the prince.
OL,12,F"It started in Estonia, a few of us
OL,13,Fofficers grew moustaches and it
OL,14,Fsnowballed from there," he said.
OL,16,F"I brought it up when I was chatting
OL,17,Fto the prince and he said 'maybe I
OL,18,Fshould get rid of the beard and just
OL,19,Fhave the moustache'."
OL,26,@tD@AOUxD@AOU{D@UO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
