PN,43904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1774620679
OL,3,CPrince of Wales jokes he may ditch
OL,4,Cbeard for moustache after meeting
OL,5,Ctroops
OL,7,FWilliam also joked with Maxine
OL,8,FDebonnaire, 63, from Gillingham, Kent
OL,9,Fand her son Lieutenant Harris
OL,10,FDebonnaire, 26, who served in Estonia.
OL,12,FMrs Debonnaire said she teased her son
OL,13,Fin front of William about how much
OL,14,Ftime they spent together when he
OL,15,Freturned from his deployment in the
OL,16,FBaltic state.
OL,18,F"He was out every night when he came
OL,19,Fback and sometimes during the day,"
OL,20,Fshe joked.
OL,26,@zD@AOU{D@cO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1774620679
OL,3,CPrince of Wales jokes he may ditch
OL,4,Cbeard for moustache after meeting
OL,5,Ctroops
OL,7,F"I'm very proud of him, very proud. I
OL,8,Fkeep telling everyone my son is an
OL,9,Fofficer in the Army."
OL,11,FThe mother and son also quizzed
OL,12,FWilliam about his love of sport,
OL,13,Fasking if he had been watching his
OL,14,Fbeloved Aston Villa football club and
OL,15,Fwhich did he prefer, football or
OL,16,Frugby, with the prince answering
OL,17,Ffootball.
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@UO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
