OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1774620679
OL,3,CPrince of Wales jokes he may ditch
OL,4,Cbeard for moustache after meeting
OL,5,Ctroops
OL,7,FLt Debonnaire was also sporting a
OL,8,Fbushy moustache and said he had been
OL,9,Fthe first among the officers deployed
OL,10,Fto Estonia to grow one, originally for
OL,11,Fthe Movember charity campaign.
OL,13,F"It just grew on me", he joked.
OL,26,@uD@AOUuD@TO]
